Ward/block name: Name of the ward (if city) or block (if reporting body is a district) for which details are being provided (string)
Ward number (if applicable): Ward number for which details are being provided (integer)
Total cases: cumulative cases in the region upto the date specified (integer)
Active cases: number of active cases as on date (integer)
Mild cases (isolated): number of active cases who are isolated in facilities, as on date (integer)
Moderate cases (hospitalized): number of active cases who are currently hospitalized  or in covid health care centers (integer)
Severe cases (In ICU): number of active cases who are in intensive care units as on date (integer)
Critical cases (ventilated patients): number of active cases who are currently on ventilators as on date (integer)
Recovered cases: cumulative number of recovered cases as on date (integer)
Fatalities: cumulative number of fatalities as on date (integer)
